The paper deals with the problem of improving the performance of deep networks in computer vision tasks, which is a common topic in the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) communities. The proposed method involves the aggregation of multiple weak classifiers, which is a technique commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of boosting algorithms, which are a popular technique in neural networks (cs.NE) research.
